{"tid":1020573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭政府禁華為5G    華為竟在當地主要報紙刊全版廣告嘲諷","createTime":"2019-02-13T16:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T13:11:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":221,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"21f246b57106cb82397e5d88449974eeb629a8ba","tid":1020573,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:34:30.000Z","msg":"自紐西蘭政府以國家安全為由，禁止中國電信華為參與當地5G網路基礎建設，華為今日在當地主要報紙刊登全版廣告，稱：「沒有華為的5G就像紐西蘭沒有橄欖球一樣」藉由紐西蘭熱衷的橄欖球運動，來批評紐西蘭政府禁止華為參與網路建設的決策。<br />\n<br />\n根據綜合外媒報導，愈來愈多國家針對華為頒布禁令，原因是擔心華為設備可能成為中國間諜的後門，像是英國正在考慮該科技公司的設備在參與建設中的作用，德國政府於今年1月召開會議，評估該公司所構成的風險，紐西蘭情報局在去年11月以國家安全理由，禁止華為參與當地5G網路基礎建設計劃，但北京政府反駁這些疑慮都是假的。<br />\n<br />\n華為紐西蘭分部的副總安德魯鮑威爾（Andrew Bowater）表示，政府不願意進行任何有關這禁令的對話，華為應該得到解釋。「沒有證據表明華為有任何不當行為，我們強烈反對任何有關華為業務影響紐西蘭安全的觀點，我們應該有解釋疑慮的機會」<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭對外情報部門「政府通訊安全局」（GCSB）局長李特（Andrew Little）表示：「華為的舉動對這事情沒有任何的幫助，我們要對紐西蘭的國家安全利益做出最好決定，這是我做任何決策的唯一考量。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2698158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2698158&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyETk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=0ba9f98e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2698158&h=9f2f6d70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2698158</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzOUlb7V4AAEDXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzOUlb7V4AAEDXa.jpg&h=f6e20c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/02/13/huawei-ads-in-new-zealand-newspapers-say-5g-ban-will-hit-customers.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2019%2F02%2F13%2Fhuawei-ads-in-new-zealand-newspapers-say-5g-ban-will-hit-customers.html&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyETk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=c4f3eb03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2019/02/13/huawei-ads-in-new-zealand-newspapers-say-5g-ban-will-hit-customers.html</a>"},{"pid":"a53a0712f5da5e93dec619c3c01a8245746e406e","tid":1020573,"uid":51620,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 射到成地都係"},{"pid":"979ac7d3c747a96959d053bf32e9eeac4a61bc29","tid":1020573,"uid":37869,"like":303,"dislike":1,"score":302,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"華為係咪已經痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6367b17d3bf9ca38fd2df336e4097b91d2288344","tid":1020573,"uid":49853,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"小氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68c30ca56d5d4d611ea73f9d0e003806a3884c6","tid":1020573,"uid":197920,"like":334,"dislike":2,"score":332,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"Or World Cup without China ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76560a1c993f0e27b2be50acb3cc4006167c9b4","tid":1020573,"uid":7369,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"咁搞咪仲多人憎"},{"pid":"097440dd4d41ed7ed31bcbc52a3b9297891549af","tid":1020573,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"Up乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e90314ec2d03e8991fa32cd62835fb04913bb3","tid":1020573,"uid":152476,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"發爛渣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6